{"tid":435984,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"女友中六畢業就出左黎做野 生活好苦悶","createTime":"2017-10-14T18:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T17:35:43.000Z","uid":138728,"like":84,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"630afe0944bf24b35a6e4fcc49a52c36ac7e30e7","tid":435984,"uid":138728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:02:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 女友之前因某啲原因冇考齊DSE<br />\n又唔想做毅進仔 所以佢就出左黎做野<br />\n而家係一間畫室仔教緊小朋友畫畫<br />\n番6日放1日 做得都尚算開心  <br />\n但係佢個人開始愈黎愈頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就連放假都唔多想郁<br />\n但其實佢有好多地方想去  但偏偏就冇咁既精力<br />\n之前就話一班Friend 點都有地方去下<br />\n但佢最Friend 既朋友全部都繼讀讀書 有自己新既圈子<br />\n我都唔例外 一個星期都係陪到佢一兩日 <br />\n宜家佢既生活得番 番工 放工 放假頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想令佢恢復番好似以前咁咁活潑好動<br />\n巴打們有咩建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8700f1890119725b7bb5af90e81dcc6974df15b1","tid":435984,"uid":11040,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:04:25.000Z","msg":"讀返書"},{"pid":"1befff4349ddb25cea1f84d24c06edfe22586ceb","tid":435984,"uid":80015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"一至6 陪埋佢"},{"pid":"16912fdf42db2f233893051f28c43d9ecc888bd3","tid":435984,"uid":138728,"like":2,"dislike":25,"score":-23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:08:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀返書</blockquote><br />\n佢好明顯唔係讀書既材料 我都唔想佢再讀番折磨佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d90a49edaf978638f3ed6143d8cc1e6d24e952f","tid":435984,"uid":10788,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀返書</blockquote><br />\n佢好明顯唔係讀書既材料 我都唔想佢再讀番折磨佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀art"},{"pid":"8fff1e7bbd5d63922b8784d790eac90f23ed9ec1","tid":435984,"uid":41737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T18:09:4